{"tid":1379702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好癱瘓路面交通","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T00:09:19.000Z","uid":287461,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3113dab4f222bac9684b68b7b7f5b688e034c1","tid":1379702,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:45:24.000Z","msg":"非反話<br />\n<br />\n之前見到有巴打想係路上狂開死火燈，癱瘓路面交通。<br />\n<br />\n但如果真係咁樣做嘅話，首當其衝嘅係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救護同消防服務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以諗都唔好諗"},{"pid":"860c824f482b1f5681dc6c8bcf81b9f177bdac8b","tid":1379702,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:45:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c1d1d5ea503dd601c7204b8099fe5a4c63cad27","tid":1379702,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:53:21.000Z","msg":"諗都唔好諗啊"},{"pid":"f8d3c9205643e59a15cdc3967857325b704bf904","tid":1379702,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d346b6fa1e82e8fbebe81d3bf10c602f23c76544","tid":1379702,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:09:19.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足</span></span> <br />\n大家緊記宗旨唔好被輕易帶動! <br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}